data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful single-story located in the highly desirable Apple Creek subdivision. Home is spacious; perfect for first-time buyer. Pride of ownership shows throughout this three bedroom, two full bathroom home. The kitchen boasts beautiful, well-maintained counter tops and updated light fixtures. The primary bedroom welcomes you with a beautiful bay window and ceiling fan. Relax in the garden tub or updated walk-in shower and double vanity in your en-suite. Enjoy the evening in your backyard after a long day of work under the lighted pergola. Home is walking distance to neighborhood amenity center featuring pool, clubhouse, playground, sports court, and dog park. This neighborhood feeds into the award-winning Northside ISD schools. With easy access to Medical Center, USAA, UTSA, and more, this home won't last long!
